Isifo segciwane rrhagic fever yisifo esihlasela abantu ngegciwane leEbola.le-Ebola (EVD) noma I-Ebola hemo<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Izimpawu zaso zijwayele ukuqala ezinsukwini ezimbili kuya emavikini amathathu emva kokuthintana negciwane nemfiva, umphimbo obuhlungu, i-Myalgia, ubuhlungu bemisipha, kanye nekhanda elibuhlungu. <!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Ngokujwayelekile, isicanucanu, ukubuyisa kanye nokukhishwa yisisu kuyalandela, kanjalo nokwehla kwamandla okusebenza kwesibindi kanye nezinso.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Lapho-ke abanye abantu baye baqalwe yizinkinga zokopha.<ref name=WHO2014>{{cite web|title=Ebola virus disease Fact sheet N°103|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs103/en/|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=12 April 2014|date=March 2014}}</ref>

<!-- Cause and Diagnosis-->
Igciwane lingatholakala ngokuthinta igazi noma uketshezi lwasemzimbeni lwesilwane esithelelekile ngokujwayelekile izinkawu noma amalulwane ezithelo.<ref name=WHO2014/>Ukusabalala ngomoya akukaqoshwa ngokwemvelo.<ref name=WHOAir2014>{{cite web|title=2014 Ebola Virus Disease (EVD) outbreak in West Africa|url=http://www.who.int/ith/updates/20140421/en/|website=WHO|accessdate=3 August 2014|date=Apr 21 2014}}</ref>Amalulwane ezithelo kukholakala ukuthi athwala aphinde asabalalise igciwane ngaphandle kokutheleleka.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Uma abantu sebethelelekile, isifo sithathelana phakathi kwabantu ngokunjalo.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Abesilisa abasindile basengadlulisa isifo ngesidoda isikhathi esingaba izinyanga ezimbili.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Ukuze kwenziwe ukuxilonga okuyikho, kuye kudingeke ukuba kuqinisekiswe ukuthi izifo ezinezimpawu ezifanayo njengomalaleveva, ikholera kanye nezinye izifo zegciwane lemfiva yokopha azikho.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Ukuqinisekisa ukuxilongwa okushaya khona amasampula egazi ahlolelwa igciwane, kuhlolwe izivikelamzimba, igciwane le-RNA, noma igciwane uqobo lwalo.<ref name=WHO2014/>

<!-- Prevention -->
Izindlela zokuvikela zibandakanya ukunciphisa ukusabalala kwesifo kusuka ezinkawini ezithelelekile kanye nezingulube kuya ebantwini.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Lokhu kungenziwa ngokuhlola ukuthi izilwane ezinjengalezi azithelelekile yini zibulawe bese izidumbu zazo zingcwatshwe ngendlela uma isifo sitholakele.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Ukupheka inyama ngendlela efanele kanye nokugqoka izimpahla zokuvikela lapho kuphathwa inyama nacho kungasiza.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->kanjalo nokugqoka izimpahla zokuvikela kanye nokugeza izandla lapho useduze nomuntu onaso isifo.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Amasampula oketshezi lwasemzimbeni kanye nezicubu ezinesifo kufanele kuphathwe ngokuqikelela okukhulu.<ref name=WHO2014/>

<!-- Treatment, Prognosis and Epidemiology-->
Alikho ikhambi eliqondile lokwelapha lesi sifo; <ref name=WHO2014/>Isifo lesi sibulala izindimbane zabantu: siye sibulale ama-50% kanye nama-90% alabo abasuke sebethelelekile ngegciwane laso. <ref name=WHO2014/><ref name="Elsevier/Academic Press">{{cite book|author1=C.M. Fauquet|title=Virus taxonomy classification and nomenclature of viruses; 8th report of the International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses|date=2005|publisher=Elsevier/Academic Press|location=Oxford|isbn=9780080575483|page=648|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=9Wy7Jgy5RWYC&pg=PA648}}</ref>Saqala ukubonakala e-Sudan kanye nase-Democratic Republic of Congo.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> -->Isifo sivame ukuba sivumbuke ezindaweni ezingasolwandle lwe-Sub-Saharan Africa.<ref name=WHO2014/>Kusukela ngowe-1976 (lapho yabonakala khona okokuqala) kuze kube ngowezi-2013, yingcosana engaphansi kwe-1,000 yabantu abatheleleke ngonyaka.<ref name=WHO2014/><ref name=MMWRJune2014>{{cite web|title=Ebola Viral Disease Outbreak — West Africa, 2014|url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm6325a4.htm?s_cid=mm6325a4_w|website=CDC|accessdate=26 June 2014|date=June 27, 2014}}</ref>Isiga esikhulukazi sokuqubuka kwalesi sifo yilesi esiqhubekayo [Ukuqubuka kwe-Ebola eNtshonalanga Afrika ngowezi-2014]], nokuthinta I-Guinea, Sierra Leone, Liberia kanye-ke ne-Nigeria.<ref name=CDC2014>{{cite web|title=CDC urges all US residents to avoid nonessential travel to Liberia, Guinea, and Sierra Leone because of an unprecedented outbreak of Ebola.|url=http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/notices/warning/ebola-liberia|website=CDC|accessdate=2 August 2014|date=July 31, 2014}}</ref><ref name=CDCAug2014N>{{cite web|title=Outbreak of Ebola in Guinea, Liberia, and Sierra Leone|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/outbreaks/guinea/index.html|website=CDC|accessdate=5 August 2014|date=August 4, 2014}}</ref>Kusukela ngo-August 2014 bangaphezu kwezi-1600 abantu abatholakale nalesi sifo.<ref>{{cite web|title=Ebola virus disease update - West Africa|url=http://www.who.int/csr/don/2014_08_04_ebola/en/|website=WHO|accessdate=6 August 2014|date=Aug 4, 2014}}</ref>Imizamo yokuthola ikhambi isaqhubeka; kodwa-ke okwamanje, alikatholakali.<ref name=WHO2014/>

